1. Go to https://discord.com/developers/applications

2. Create "New Application"

3. Go to "Bot" and select "Add Bot"

4. Go to "OAuth2", check "bot" and add "Administrator" permission.

5. Go to "General information and copy the bot token"

6. Copy the link and paste it onto browser. Do the prompt and choose the server to add the minigames in.

7. Download the code

8. Create a new file named ".env" with "no extension" extension.

9. type "DISCORD_BOT={your_token}", replacing {your_token} with the token you copied earlier.

10. Run the following commands:
    1. pip install -U discord
    2. pip install -U dotenv
    3. python mainBot.py
    
11. You're good to go. Enjoy!
